	<h2>Places to eat</h2>
	<p><a href="http://www.thelockinn.co.uk">The Lock Inn cafe</a> - Just basic greasy spoon food but amazing surroundings. You can even eat inside a moored canal boat on the canal. Giant fry-ups available.</p>

	<p><a href="http://www.hartley-farm.co.uk">Hartley Farm</a> - Farm shop with a good cafe. Has amazing deli goodies.</p>

	<p><a href="http://www.thenewinnwestwood.co.uk">The New Inn</a> - Pub with food.</p>

	<p><a href="http://www.hungerfordarms.co.uk">Hungerford Arms</a> - Pub that should be better than it is. Sunday lunch was pretty ropey. Fine for beer in the sun and walking distance from the Farleigh Hungerford wild swimming club.</p>

	<p><a href="http://www.poplarsinn.co.uk">The Poplars</a> - Good pub, great food. Saturday brunch with the groom will be here.</p>
